The partnership will tip off Monday on NTV when Team LeBron takes on Team Durant in the 70th NBA All-Star Game at 2:30 a.m. EAT.NTV will broadcast more than 25 live games throughout the second half of the 2020-21 NBA season. Basketball fanatics have every reason to tune in to your favorite station, NTV, after the National Basketball Association (NBA) shook hands on a historic deal with the Nation Media Group (NMG) to air select matches of the most popular basketball competition in the world. 

This multi-year deal makes NTV, which is one of the leading stations in Kenya, the official free-to-air-broadcast partner of the NBA in Kenya. 



